title: A Walk on the Wild Side
It Only Hurts for a Little While
Trial by Peers
description: While working as a parking valet, Andrew is framed for duplicating keys and burglarizing patrons' houses. Andrew chooses to have his case tried in teen court, where the jury and counsel are comprised of peers supervised by an actual judge. When Kirk pulls some strings to become Andrew's defense counsel, Andrew is unsure whether or not he is good hands.

title: A Life in the Day of Dr. J
A Bank, a Holdup, a Robber, and a Hero
